Class Album

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Album
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Album
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Model Class representing an album. An album has a owner and it contains a set of pictures. Album also has a title.
    Author:
    Dev Patel and Eric Chan
    See Also:
